  PENDING_PAYMENT
  PAID
  SUBMITTED
  ACCEPTED
  CONTENT_REQUESTED
  CONTENT_CREATION
  CONTENT_READY
  CUSTOMER_REVIEW
  APPROVED
  PUBLISHED
  VERIFIED
  DELIVERED
  SETTLED
  COMPLETED
  CANCELLED
  REFUNDED
  DISPUTED
